title: Civic Centers, Florida, 2008
name: Civic Centers, Florida, 2008
description: This dataset contains 2008 Civic Center Facility Information for the State of Florida. This dataset contains fields denoting the physical address and contact information for civic center facilities based on data taken from the Yellow and Super Pages Online. This data is meant to be used for planning purposes only and is not intended to represent a 100% inventory of civic centers in Florida. This dataset is an update to the gc_civiccenter_sep05.shp layer.
